text: The Taichung Bank Club is a Taiwanese volleyball club. They have represented Chinese Taipei in international club volleyball competitions. They participated at the 2016 Asian Women's Club Volleyball Championship under the name "T. Grand". Their men's team has won the 2015 Asian Men's Club Volleyball Championship without losing a single match, beating Qatari club Al-Arabi in the final, thus qualifying for the 2016 FIVB Volleyball Men's Club World Championship. ==Roster== ;2016 Asian Women's Club Volleyball Championship Head coach: Lo Chung-jen {|class="wikitable sortable" style="font-size:100%; text- align:center;" |- !No. !style="width:12em"|Name !style="width:8em"|Date of birth !style="width:9em"|Height !style="width:9em"|Weight !style="width:9em"|Spike !style="width:9em"|Block |- | 1 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 2 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 3 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 4 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 6 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 7 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 8 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 9 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 10 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 11 ||align=left| ()||align=right||||||||| |- | 12 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 13 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 14 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 15 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 17 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 18 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |- | 19 ||align=left| ||align=right||||||||| |} ==Honors== ;Asian Men's Club Volleyball Championship *Champions: 2015 ==References== Category:Taichung Bank Category:Taiwanese volleyball clubs
